title: Spacious Newly Renovated 4 Bed + 2 Bath Apartment Near U of M!
posting_body: ['Beautifully renovated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment for rent near the U of M campus!', 'This pet-friendly apartment features stainless steel appliances, granite counters, in-unit laundry, and off-street parking is available.', "With a private entry and your own personal PIN code, you'll feel right at home in this apartment.", 'Conveniently located within walking distance to the University of Minnesota, this apartment is also only minutes from Northeast Minneapolis, the Como area shops and restaurants, downtown, and St. Anthony Main. 35W, I-94, and bus lines are also nearby.', 'Features:', '- Dishwasher', '- In-unit washer/dryer', '- 24/7 Emergency Maintenance', '- Completely Renovated', '- High-end granite counter-tops', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Two stories with bedrooms on both levels', 'Applications: $50/person', 'Deposit: $500/person', 'Pet Fee: $250', 'Pet Deposit: $250', 'Pet Rent: $50']
